title: 820-02020 PPBUS is floating
message:
Hello,everybody!

I have another Macbook Pro 13 A2338 , Board 820-02020 no power, no liquid damaged

PPBUS_AON is floating constantly like I have shortage . 

I've removed the F5200 and have good voltage on C5250 

I've tried to inject some volts on this rail , but no current consumption...

In diod mode I have 600 ohm (if red on the ground) and nothing in another way

What's it be?

title: 820-02020 PPBUS is floating
message:
3V8_AON pulsing too?
Also check U8100 and U7700 LDOs.

title: 820-02020 PPBUS is floating
message:
3V8_AON is stable, 3.8 volts
But PPBUS_AON is floating constantly from 7v to 12,3v

title: 820-02020 PPBUS is floating
message: Compare diode mode readings on all power rails with good board, or OpenBoardData reference table.
